Capital Markets

Company Overview of Hourglass Capital, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hourglass Capital, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services primarily to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also manages private pooled investment funds. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It uses Long/Short and Short strategies to make its investments. The firm invests in value and growth stocks and investment grade and non-investment grade fixed income securities. It employs a c...
Hourglass Capital, LLC is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services primarily to high net worth individuals. It also caters to individuals, pension and profit sharing plans, investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, and corporations. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also manages private pooled investment funds. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. It uses Long/Short and Short strategies to make its investments. The firm invests in value and growth stocks and investment grade and non-investment grade fixed income securities. It employs a combination of quantitative and qualitative analysis with top-down and bottom-up approach to make its investments. Hourglass Capital, LLC was founded in 1989 and is based in Houston, Texas.
Detailed Description


