We are able to personalize most of our hourglasses for that special occasion, gift or corporate award. Depending on which hourglass you choose designs can be etched into the endcaps OR engraved plates can be attached to the inside of the endcaps or attached to the top of the endcaps. You're only limited by your imagination!
          
Please contact us at 800-690-1938 or cs@justhourglasses.com with your special order needs and we will do our best to accommodate you!
 









