Hourglass and Sand Timer Kits You Assemble



Featured
Best Selling
Alphabetically: A-Z
Alphabetically: Z-A
Price: Low to High
Price: High to Low
Date: New to Old
Date: Old to New







A select number of our hourglasses can be sent to you in kit form so you can add your own sand (or other material) to your hourglass.  
We highly recommend reading through our FAQ page before making your selection to clarify how our kits work by clicking here.
What's Included:

Frame for hourglass, disassembled
Glass globe: 

Empty globe with no sand (less accurate with larger center hole to accommodate most types of sand)  OR
Globe with tan sand included  (only available with Signature Collection hourglasses) 



Assembly Instructions
Epoxy and metal cap for sealing the glass globe once filled.

What's NOT Included:

Wood glue or epoxy needed for frame (not necessary for all of them)
Funnel
Sand*
Engraving (available separately - see options)


*Signature Collection hourglasses are available with tan sand as an option. We also have sand available for purchase if you click here










